\id 2CO Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular
\mt1 ∆ÅATAKURU PUULUSA ∆äIMMURU HAA E ∆ÅE KORENTI ∆ÅEN
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, mo Alla hoddiri wonugol *sahaabaajo Iisaa Almasiihu on, wondude e oo musi…ó…óo wi'etee…óo Timotee, haa e ngal *moftal Alla wongal Korenti, e gom…óin…ìe won…ìe Akaaya …ìen fow.
\v 2 Yo mo∆¥∆¥ere e …ìuttu wonan on immorde e Alla Baaba men, e Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on.
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Jarniri Allaahu, Wakkilinoowo on
\p 
\v 3 Mantoore wonanii Alla, Ben Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, on Baabaajo yurmetee…óo e on Alla Jom wakkilaare fow,
\v 4 on wakkilinoowo en e nder kala tampereeji men, fii no enen kadi waawiren wakkilinirde …ìen won…ìe e nder kala noone tampereeji wakkilaare nde he…ìir…óen Alla nden enen tigi.
\v 5 Ko fii, ko wano tampereeji *Almasiihu on layirta e hoore men non, ko wano non wakkilaare men nden layirta immorde e Almasiihu on.
\v 6 Si tawii men tampii, ko fii wakkilaare mon nden e fii kisiyee mon on. Si tawii men wakkilinaama, ko fii no wakkilinire…óon, no wawnire…óon ≈ãa…≤…≤aade tampereeji gooti e …ói men woni na…ìude …óin.
\v 7 Tama'u amen on e telen-ma mon ko sellu…óo, ko fii me…óen andi, wano tawdira…óon non e tampereeji amen …óin, ko wano non tawdira…óon e wakkilaare amen nden.
\p 
\v 8 Men faalaaka yo on ronku andude, yo musi…ì…ìe amen, tampereeji he…ìu…ói men …óin *Aazii …ói men sonjiraa, haa ka tawata alaa hattoode toonin doole amen …óen, haa men ta∆¥ii hay wuurugol.
\v 9 Kono menen e hoore amen tigi, me…óen felliti men fawaama mayde, fii wota men fawu hoolaare amen nden e hoore amen menen tigi, kono e Alla on Immintinoowo may…ìe …ìen.
\v 10 Ko on jattini men, jattinoyta men kadi e sifa nden mayde. Hiiyii, me…óen tan∆¥inii, o jattinoyay men
\v 11 e nder ko faaborton men torndeeji kon. Ko non Alla jaabinirta torndeeji …ói …óuu…óu…ìe torantoo men …óin. Ko …óun wa…ói si yim…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe jarnay Alla fii amen.
\s1 Fii no Puulusa ∆Åanginiri ko Ha…ói o Yiltitoo Korenti
\p 
\v 12 Ko men woni mantorde kon, ko ko …ìernde amen nden …ìanginani men kon, wonde men wuuririi e oo aduna, tentinii telen-ma mon, nun…óal e haqiiqa ko iwri ka Alla, hara hinaa ko iwri e faamu ne…ó…óanke, kono ko e sulfu Alla on.
\v 13 Ko fii ko men woni on windande kon fow, ko ko waawoton jangude faamon. E mi…óo tan∆¥inii on faamay …óun fota,
\v 14 wano fu…ó…óor…óon faamude non wonde ko men …ìe mantorton. Onon kadi ko on …ìe men mantorta …≤ande ardu Iisaa Joomi men on.
\p 
\v 15 E nder nden hoolaare, hari mi…óo faalanoo yahude ka mon, fii no he…ìiron faabo Alla goo kadi.
\v 16 Si mi iwriino ka mon, mi fe∆¥∆¥a Masedonii. Nde mi…óo iwta Masedonii, mi artira ka mon kadi fii no walliron mi no mi hewtira ka diiwal Yahuuda.
\v 17 E nder anniyagol an …óun, taw si hara mi miijitaaki? Kaa hara on sikku …óen e…ì…ìooje an ko e…ì…ìooje ne…ó…óanke, haa ka tawata no e an ¬´hiiyii¬ª e ¬´oo'o¬ª?
\v 18 No Alla woniri sella-findeejo non, ko non tawiri kongol ngol men hewtini on ngol wonaa ngol ¬´hiiyii¬ª e ¬´oo'o¬ª.
\v 19 Ko fii *∆Åi…ó…óo Alla on, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu on, mo min e Silaasi e Timotee men waajii on fii mun on, hinaa mo ¬´hiiyii¬ª e ¬´oo'o¬ª, kono ko ¬´hiiyii¬ª woni e makko.
\v 20 Fodooje Alla …óen fow ko ¬´hiiyii¬ª e makko, awa kadi ko kanko wi'irten Alla ¬´aamiina¬ª fii mangu makko ngun.
\v 21 Ko Alla woni fellintinanoowo en fow wonde hi…óen humondiri e Almasiihu on. Ko kanko kadi su…ìii en,
\v 22 o maandiniri en maande makko nden, …óun ko tolmugol Ruuhu makko on ka …ìer…óe men.
\p 
\v 23 Alla ko seedee an: ko fii wota mi aanin on ha…ói mi yiltitoo Korenti.
\v 24 Hinaa fii me…óen laamii on e hoore gom…óinal mon ngal, kono ko men gollidoo…ìe e mon fii weltaare mon nden, …ìay hi…óon tabiti e nder gom…óinal ngal.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Min tigi mi aadii wota mi yiltitodu ka mon e sokola.
\v 2 Ko fii min, si mi sokolinii on, haray ko hombo waawi lan weltinde, si hinaa onon he…ìir…ìe lan sokola …ìen?
\v 3 Mi windiranii on nii fii wota mi he…ìir haanu…ìe weltinde lan …ìen sokola nde mi aroyi. Mi…óo joganii on fow ndee hoolaare wonde, weltaare an nden ko nde mon on fow.
\v 4 Ko e nder annde tii…óunde e mettu …ìernde e gon…ói tii…óu…ói mi windani on, hinaa non fii sokolingol on, kono ko fii no andiron giggol tii…óungol ngol mi joganii on ngol.
\s1 Fii Yaafagol Bonnu…óo
\p 
\v 5 Si tawii go…ó…óo e mon wonii sabu annde, haray hinaa min o aanini, kono ko on fow, maa wo…ì…ìe e mon, (fii wota mi wowlu haa fe∆¥∆¥ita).
\v 6 Feloore nde …ìur…ìe …ìen e hakkunde mon fawi mo nden, yonay on ne…ó…óo.
\v 7 Haray jooni hi…óon haani mo yaafaade wakkilina, fii wota o sonjor sokola fe∆¥∆¥itu…óo.
\v 8 Awa mi torike on hollugol mo giggol.
\v 9 Ko fii, ko mi windirannoo on, ko fii ndarndagol on annda si hi…óon …óoftii ko woni woo.
\v 10 Ko fii kala mo yaafani…óon, mi yaafanto mo min kadi. Telen-ma an min, si no woodi ko mi yaafoo, ko fii mon mi yaafori, e yeeso *Almasiihu on,
\v 11 fii wota en accu Ibuliisa foola en, ko fii wonaa wa si en andaa e…ì…ìooje makko …óen.
\s1 Fii Annde Puulusa nden Turuwaasi
\p 
\v 12 Fewndo ko mi hewti Turuwaasi fii fe…≤…≤ingol Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Almasiihu on, mi tawi Joomiraa…óo on no udditanimmi dambugal.
\v 13 Kono tawi …ìernde an nden waalanooki, …ìay mi tawaali …óon oo musi…ó…óo an wi'etee…óo Tiituusa. Onsay mi waynitii …ìe, mi fokkitani Masedonii.
\p 
\v 14 Yo mantoore wonan Alla, on Won…óo en okkude polgal soono woo e nder humondiral men e Almasiihu on, on Won…óo en huutorde fii fe…≤…≤ingol nokku kala urngol andugol Almasiihu on.
\v 15 Awa e hakkunde wonaa…ìe dandeede …ìen, e hakkunde won…ìe mulude …ìen, hi…óen wa'ani Alla wa angiri uurundi ndi Almasiihu on wee…ìitani mo:
\v 16 hi…óen wonani wo…ì…ìe …ìen barngol mayde nawrayngol e mayde, hi…óen wonani …ìeya …ìen urngol ngurndan nawrayngol e ngurndan. Ko ne…ó…óo hombo gaynata sifa …óen golle?
\v 17 Ko fii men wa'aa wa wo…ì…ìe, baanor…ìe daaluyee Alla on, kono ko e nder haqiiqa men yewtirta e innde Alla, e yeeso Alla e nder humondiral amen e Almasiihu on.
\c 3
\s1 Fii Yangantoo…ìe Ahadi Heyri ndin
\p 
\v 1 E hara men fu…ó…óitoto fahin kuljude hoore amen? Kaa men hatonjinay e …ìataake kulju…óe fii amen wano wo…ì…ìe goo? Kaa ko onon haani wa…óangol men …óun?
\v 2 Ko onon tigi woni …ìatakuru amen, windiindu ka …ìer…óe amen, ndu yim…ìe …ìen fow jangi, faami.
\v 3 No laa…ìi, ko on …ìatakuru *Almasiihu on, ndu menen tigi men yottini, ndu tawata hinaa ndaha windiraa, kono ko windiraandu Ruuhu Alla Wuuru…óo on, ndu tawata hinaa e hoore alluuje kaa∆¥e windaa, kono ko ka …ìer…óe mon.
\p 
\v 4 Ko …óun woni hoolaare nde men jogii immorde e Almasiihu on yeeso Alla.
\v 5 Hinaa wonde me…óen mari feere wa…óugol go…ó…óun menen tigi, wa ko iwrata e mbawdi amen menen tigi. Kono mbawdi amen ndin ko e Alla iwri.
\v 6 O wawnii men kadi wonugol yangantoo…ìe *ahadi heyri ndin, hara hinaa tippude e bindol sariya on, kono ko tippude e Ruuhu Allaahu on. Ko fii bindol ngol waray, kono Ruuhu on wurnay.
\s1 Fii Mangu Ahadi Heyri ndin
\p 
\v 7 Sariya Muusaa windiranoo…óo kalfe e hoore alluuje kaa∆¥e on arduno e ngun mangu haa ka tawata *Isra'iilayankee…ìe …ìen waawataa ndaarude yeeso Muusaa ngon sabu on annoora fe∆¥∆¥oowo wonnoo…óo ka yeeso makko. Si tawii golle on Sariya nawroowo e mayde ardii e sifa ngun mangu,
\v 8 haray ko haa honto non golle Ruuhu Allaahu on …ìuri mawnude!
\v 9 Si tawii ko nawrata en e …≤aawoore kon mawninaama, haray ittii e sikke ko haa honto ko wa…óata en feewu…ìe yeeso Alla kon …ìuri mawnude!
\v 10 Hi…óen waawi hay wi'ude wonde ngun mangu fe∆¥∆¥ungu fuutoraama mangu mun ngun fow, si ngu e…ì…ìindiraama e …ìurngu mawnude ngu hande ngun.
\v 11 Si tawii ko fe∆¥∆¥ata kon he…ìii mangu, haray ko haa honto ko luttata kon mawnata!
\p 
\v 12 Awa oo tama'u …óoo no okki en hoolaare tii…óunde.
\v 13 En wa…óirtaa wano Muusaa non, on wa…óaynoo…óo tiggaare ka yeeso mun, fii wota Isra'iilayankee…ìe …ìen yi'u rawnoode annoora makko fe∆¥∆¥oowo on.
\v 14 Kono, e nder miijooji ma…ì…ìe …óin, …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yoorii. Ko fii, haa weetaango hande ngoo, si *ahadi hinndi ndin janga, taway haa hande nden tiggaare no woodaa. Nde ittaaka, ko fii ko e Almasiihu on tun nde muti.
\v 15 Haa weetaango hande ngoo, si Sariya Muusaa on janga, taway tiggaare no wirni …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen.
\v 16 Kono si fewta e Joomiraa…óo on, taway tiggaare nden ittaama ka …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe.
\v 17 E hin-le Joomiraa…óo on ko Ruuhu, awa kadi ko ka Ruuhu Joomiraa…óo on woni …óon, ko …óon ndimu ngun woni.
\v 18 Enen, …ìe geece mun buumaaki …ìen fow, jalbir…ìe mangu Joomiraa…óo on wa ndaarorgal, hi…óen e nder wattegol mbaadi makko, mangu e hoore mangu, immorde e Joomiraa…óo on, …óun ko on Ruuhu.
\c 4
\s1 Fii Ngalu Mariingu e nder Loo…óe Leydi
\p 
\v 1 Ko …óun wa…ói, …ìay Alla ye…óii men …óen golle e nder yurmeende makko nden, maayu …ìernde he…ìataa men.
\v 2 Men sali kala ko suu…óii hersinii, men wuurirtaa kadi ∆¥oyre, men …ìoylataa kadi daaluyee Alla on, kono ko e nder ko men fe…≤…≤inta goonga on kon, …óun holnay kala …ìernde ne…ó…óanke fii amen yeeso Alla.
\v 3 Si tawii haa jooni Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o mo men waajotoo on no ni…ì…ìitii, haray ko won…ìe mulude …ìen o ni…ì…ìitani,
\v 4 …óun ko …ìen …ìe gom…óinaa, …ìe tawata alla nguu jamaanu wuminii miijooji mun, fii wota …ìe yi'u jalbeendi Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o …ìangin…óo mangu *Almasiihu on, on won…óo mbaadi Alla.
\v 5 Hinaa fii amen tigi men woni waajaade, kono ko fii Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on men woni waajaade, menen non ko men kurkaa…ói mon sabu Iisaa.
\v 6 Ko fii ko on Alla daalu…óo: ¬´Yo ndaygu ngun jalbu ka nder niwre¬ª,\f a \fr 4:6 \ft 4.6 Fu…ó. 1.3 \f* ko kanko kadi jalbini …ìer…óe amen …óen, fii ndaygingol e amen andal mangu Alla wongu e yeeso Almasiihu on ngon.
\p 
\v 7 Enen jogii…ìe ngun ngalu, hi…óen wa'i wa loo…óe leydi, fii no andiree wonde ngal bawgal mawngal ko e Alla iwi, hinaa e amen.
\v 8 Men …ìittiraama nooneeji …óin fow, kono men muncaaki. Men ji…ìii, kono men ta∆¥aaki.
\v 9 Men cukkaa, kono men hawkaaka. Men li…ìaa, kono men hayraali.
\v 10 Me…óen wondi e mayde Iisaa nden saa'i kala ka …ìalli amen, fii no ngurndan Iisaa …óan fee…≤ira ka …ìalli amen.
\v 11 Ko fii enen wur…ìe …ìen soono woo, hi…óen wee…ìitanaa mayde nden sabu Iisaa, fii no ngurndan Iisaa …óan kadi fee…≤ira e …ìalli men maayooji …óin.
\v 12 Ko non men wee…ìitorani mayde nden fii no he…ìiron ngurndan.
\p 
\v 13 Wano windori non: ¬´Mi gom…óinii, ko …óun wa…ói si mi wowli.¬ª\f b \fr 4:13 \ft 4.13 Zab. 116.10 \f* Menen kadi …ìay ko noone gom…óinal gootal men mari, me…óen gom…óini, ko …óun wa…ói si me…óen wowlude,
\v 14 e nder andugol wonde, on Immintin…óo Iisaa Joomi on, o immintiniday en kadi e Iisaa, o wee…ìitida men e mon yeeso makko.
\v 15 Ko fii, …óun fow ko woni ardude ko fii mon, fii yo sulfu on …ìurtu hewtude yim…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe, fii no yettooje …óen ka mangu Alla laatora …óuu…óu…óe.
\v 16 Ko …óun wa…ói si maayu …ìernde he…ìataa men. Hay si …ìandu amen ndun …≤olii, kono haray nder amen on no hey…óitude …≤ande woo …≤ande.
\v 17 Ko fii oo saa'i satteende e fan…óude mun, o rimanay en darja teddu…óo poomayankeejo …ìur…óo oo saa'i satteende.
\v 18 Ko fii menen, wonaa ko yi'otoo kon men wa…ói hakkilaaji amen …óin e mun, kono ko ko yi'otaako kon men wa…ói hakkillaaji amen e mun. Ko fii ko yi'otoo kon, ko ko fe∆¥∆¥ata, ko yi'otaako kon, ko ko luttata haa poomaa.
\c 5
\s1 Fii Wonunde Kammuyankeere nden
\p 
\v 1 Hi…óen andi wonde, si tawii …óii togooji …ói ho…óu…óen e mun ka leydi …óoo, (e maanaa …ìalli men …óin), aru e bonneede, haray hi…óen mari suudu ndu Alla e…ì…ìani en, …óun ko wonunde poomayankeere, nde tawata hinaa juu…óe ne…ó…óanke mo∆¥∆¥iniraa.
\v 2 Awa kadi e nder …óin togooji, hi…óen woytaade fii faale …ìornagol wonunde kammuyankeere nden,
\v 3 tawa ko en …ìornii…ìe, hara tawetaake ko en daror…ìe nii.
\v 4 Ko …óun wa…ói, enen won…ìe e nder …óin togooji, hi…óen woytaade, hi…óen sonjii, …ìay en faalaaka laataade …ìortii…ìe, kono hara ko …ìornii…ìe, fii no ngurndan …óan mo…óira mayde nden.
\v 5 Awa on Hebulin…óo en fii nden e…ì…ìoore ko Alla, on Tolmu…óo Ruuhu mun on e men.
\p 
\v 6 Awa hi…óen heewi soono woo wakkilaare. Hi…óen andi kadi fodde hi…óen wondi e nduu …ìandu, haray hi…óen wo…ó…óondiri e Joomiraa…óo on.
\v 7 Ko fii, ko gom…óinal ngal woni en ardaade, hinaa gii…óe …óen.
\v 8 Hi…óen heewi wakkilaare, ko …ìur…óen faaleede ko seedugol e nduu …ìandu ho…óa moggo Joomiraa…óo on.
\v 9 Ko …óun wa…ói, wondu…óen e nduu …ìandu maa seedu…óen e mayru, himme men …óen ko welegol Joomiraa…óo on.
\v 10 Ko fii en fow en darnete ka yeeso …≤aawirde *Almasiihu on, fii no o jonnitira mo kala njoddi kuu…óe mun …óe o wa…óunoo ka aduna, woni ko ko mo∆¥∆¥i, woni ko ko boni.
\s1 Fii Mo∆¥∆¥intingol hakkunde Yim…ìe …ìen e Alla
\p 
\v 11 Awa, …ìay men andii ko woni hulugol Joomiraa…óo on, me…óen …óa…ì…ìude no men fellintinira yim…ìe …ìen. Alla no andi ko men hom…ìe, awa mi…óo tan∆¥inii onon kadi ka nder …ìer…óe mon hi…óon andi men.
\v 12 Men alaa kuljude hoore amen kadi, kono ko dalil men woni on jonnude fii no mantoron men, fii no waawiron jaaborde …ìen won…ìe mantorde ko woni e kene kon edii …ìe mantorde ko woni e …ìernde kon.
\v 13 Si tawii ko men wilii…ìe, haray andee wonde ko fii Alla men wilanii. Si tawii kadi non me…óen selli, haray andee wonde ko fii mon men sellani.
\v 14 Ko fii giggol Almasiihu on no laamii men, menen …ìee fellitu…ìe …óun…óoo: aaden gooto maayanii fow, awa fow maayii.
\v 15 O maayanii fow, fii wota wur…ìe …ìen wuuran hoore mun hande kadi, kono yo wuuran May…óo immintinaa fii ma…ì…ìe on.
\p 
\v 16 ∆äun haray gila jooni men jogoraa hay gooto e noone no yim…ìe oo aduna jogorta go…ó…óo non. Hay si tawiino hari men jogoriino Almasiihu on wano non, jooni men jogoraa mo non hande kadi.
\v 17 Si tawii go…ó…óo no humondiri e Almasiihu on, haray ko o tagudi heyri, haray piiji ki…ó…ói …óin fe∆¥∆¥irii mo, haray piiji …óin fow wontii kesi.
\v 18 ∆äun fow ko immorde e Alla woni, on Mo∆¥∆¥intin…óo hakkunde men e makko rewrude e Almasiihu on. O ye…ói men menen kadi golle mo∆¥∆¥intingol hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen e makko kanko Alla.
\v 19 Ko fii Alla mo∆¥∆¥intinii hakkunde makko e aduna on rewrude e Almasiihu on, e …ìaawo joganagol yim…ìe …ìen bonnereeji ma…ì…ìe …óin, o halfinii men menen kadi kongol mo∆¥∆¥intingol hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen e makko.
\v 20 Awa ko men …ìe Almasiihu on immini\f c \fr 5:20 \ft 5.20 \it ¬´Ko men …ìe Almasiihu on immini¬ª\it* no firi \it ¬´ambassadeurs¬ª\it* e haala Gereeki.\f* wa si tawii Alla no rewrude e amen fii waajagol. Awa men jeejii on e innde Almasiihu on: wonee welditu…ìe e Alla.
\v 21 On mo junuubu alaa e mun, …óun ko Iisaa Almasiihu on, Alla wa…óii mo junuubu fii men, fii, sabu humondiral men e Almasiihu on, no woniren feewu…ìe Alla.
\c 6
\p 
\v 1 ∆Åay ko men gollidoo…ìe, men wakkilinii on wota on ja…ìir sulfu Alla on meere.
\v 2 Ko fii himo daali:
\q1 ¬´Mi jaabinanii ma ka saa'i sulfu,
\q1 ka …≤alaande kisiyee mi faabike ma.¬ª\f d \fr 6:2 \ft 6.2 Isa. 49.8 \f*
\m Awa mi andinii on ko fewndo …óoo woni saa'i sulfu on, awa kadi ko …≤alaande kisiyee nden nii.
\s1 Fii Tampereeji Puulusa …óin
\p 
\v 3 Awa men wonataa sabu peggal woo e hoore hay gooto, fii wota golle amen …óen wonu huunde felniinde.
\v 4 E kala huunde men …ìanginay ko men kurkantoo…ìe Alla, e nder ≈ãa…≤…≤an…óe buy, e nder tampereeji …óin e ≈ãakkireede, e nder anndeeji,
\v 5 e nder pigge e kaseede e murtaneede, e golleeji sattu…ói e angal …óoyngol e heege.
\v 6 Me…óen fe…≤…≤inira …óun laa…ìal e gandal e mu…≤al e mo∆¥∆¥uki e *Ruuhu Senii…óo on e giggol ngol alaa faasiqankaaku,
\v 7 wondude e daaluyee goongaajo on e baw…óe Alla …óen, peewal ngal wona aala amen ha…ìir…óo e hiwitor…óo.
\v 8 E hoore me…óen teddinee e me…óen hoynee, me…óen wowlee ko boni e me…óen wowlee ko mo∆¥∆¥i. Me…óen jogoree wa fenoo…ìe, hara-le ko men wowloo…ìe goonga.
\v 9 Men jogoree wa …ìe andaaka fii kala me…óen andaa, wa won…ìe maayude e hin-le me…óen wuuri, maa wa wonaa…ìe letteede fii kala men waraaka,
\v 10 wa sokolnaa…ìe e hin-le saa'i kala me…óen weltii, wa …ìillii…ìe hara-le me…óen al…óinde …óuu…óu…ìe, wa …ìe alaa huunde e hin-le me…óen mari fow.
\p 
\v 11 Ko onon yo …ìe Korenti, men haalanii on ko woni e amen kon, me…óen ya…≤…≤ani on …ìer…óe amen …óen.
\v 12 Men faa…óinanaali on …ìer…óe amen …óen, kono ko onon tigi faa…óinani men …ìer…óe mon …óen.
\v 13 Awa mi…óo yewtira on wa fay…ìe an: onon kadi wa…óiranee men wano men wa…óirani on non, udditanon men …ìer…óe mon …óen!
\s1 Fii Wo…ó…óitagol ko Boni
\p 
\v 14 Wota on humondir e …ìe gom…óinaa …ìen. Ko fii ko humondiral hongal woni hakkunde peewal ngal e angal peewal ngal? Maa ko kawtital hongal woni hakkunde ndaygu e niwre?
\v 15 E ko nanondiral hongal woni hakkunde *Almasiihu on e Ibuliisa?\f …ó \fr 6:15 \ft 6.15 Ndee innde Ibuliisa …óoo e haala Gereeki ko \it ¬´Beliyar¬ª.\it*\f* E ko ge…ìal hongal gom…óin…ìe …ìen e …ìe gom…óinaa …ìen hawti?
\v 16 E ko *ahadi hondi wondi suudu Alla ndun e sanamuuji …óin? Ko fii, ko enen woni suudu Alla Wuuru…óo on, wano Alla daaliri non:
\q1 ¬´Mi ho…óay, mi jinda hakkunde ma…ì…ìe,
\q1 mi wona Alla ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wona jamaa an.¬ª\f e \fr 6:16 \ft 6.16 Lew. 26.11-12 e Haz. 37.27 \f*
\p 
\v 17 Ko …óun wa…ói si Joomiraa…óo on daali:
\q1 ¬´Iwee e hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, seedon,
\q1 wota on meemu ko laa…ìaa,
\q1 min mi ja…ì…ìoyto on.
\p 
\v 18 ¬´Mi wonanay on Baaba,
\q1 onon wonanon mi …ìi…ì…ìe wor…ìe e …ìi…ì…ìe rew…ìe.
\q1 Ko Joomiraa…óo Jom Bawgal on daali …óun.¬ª\f f \fr 6:18 \ft 6.17-18 Isa. 52.11, Haz. 20.34-41, 2Sam. 7.8-14 \f*
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 ∆Åay non hi…óen mari wano …óii fodaariiji, yo yi…ì…ìe, la…ì…ìino…óen e kala ko tuuninta …ìandu ndun e ruuhu on, e hoore timmingol laa…ìal ngal e nder kulol Alla.
\s1 Fii Tuubuubuyee …ìe Korenti …ìen e Weltaare Puulusa nden
\p 
\v 2 Wernee men ka …ìer…óe mon, ko fii men faw…≤aaki hay e gooto, men bonnaali kadi hay gooto, awa kadi men huutoraali hay gooto.
\v 3 Hinaa fii felugol on mi wi'iri …óun, ko fii hari mi wi'uno wonde hi…óon ka …ìer…óe amen, woni ngurndan, woni mayde.
\v 4 Mi…óo mari hoolaare tii…óunde e telen-ma mon, mi…óo mari ko mi mantora fii mon fota, mi…óo wakkilinaa fota, mi…óo heewi weltaare e nder …óii satteendeeji amen fow.
\p 
\v 5 Ko fii gila men hewti Masedonii, men he…ìaali feere no men fowtora hay see…óa, men tampiniraama noone fow, gere ka kene, kulol ka nder.
\v 6 Kono Alla, Wakkilinoowo miskin…ìe …ìen, o wakkilinirii men ardu Tiituusa ndun.
\v 7 Wonaa non ardu makko ndun tun o wakkiliniri men, kono kadi, ko wakkilaare nde wakkilin…óon mo nden. O sifanike men faale mon tii…óu…óo on e gon…ói mon …óin e cataare mon nden fii an. ∆äun wa…ói haa weltaare an nden …ìurti tii…óude.
\p 
\v 8 Hay si tawii mi sokolinirii on …ìatakuru an ndun, mi ninsaa …óun jooni, hay si tawii mi…óo ninsunoo. Ko fii mi…óo sutii wonde ndun …ìatakuru ko sokolini on ko haa see…óa.
\v 9 Fewndo …óoo mi…óo weltii, hinaa non fii ko sokol…óon kon, kono ko fii ko sokola mon on addi on e tuubuubuyee kon, ko fii on sokoliniraama no Alla yi…óiri, …ìay on he…ìiraali men bone woo.
\v 10 Ko …óun wa…ói, sokola mo Alla yi…ói on adday tuubuubuyee nawroowo e kisiyee mo en ninsataa, e hin-le sokola oo aduna ko addata ko mayde.
\v 11 Awa on yi'ii ko oo sokola mo Alla yi…ói wa…ói e mon kon: …óun ko wakkilaare, e faale danditagol too…≤e, e ko tikku…óon kon, e ko ≈ãal…óu…óon fii bone wa…óaa…óo on, e faale mon mo∆¥∆¥o fii yi'itugol lan, e cataare mon nden, e hebulaare mon nden fii donkingol bonnu…óo on. On holliri noone fow wonde on tawaaka e nduu muraadu.
\v 12 Awa si mi windanii on, hinaa sabu faw…≤ii…óo on, maa faw…≤aa…óo e mun on, kono ko fii no jogitor…óon men non fee…≤irana on onon tigi yeeso Alla.
\v 13 Ko …óun wa…ói si men wakkilinaa. Kono e hoore nden wakkilaare amen, men …ìurti weltorde weltaare nde Tiituusa weltinaa nden, on mo on fow weltin…óon …ìernde mun.
\v 14 Si tawii mi mantorii fii mon yeeso makko see…óa, haray mi hersiraa …óun, kono ko wano ko men yewtata on saa'i woo kon woniri goonga non, ko non ko men mantori moggo Tiituusa kon woniri kadi goonga.
\v 15 Awa kadi giggol ngol o joganii on ngol ko tii…óungol, tuma kala o anditi ko …óofti…óon mo kon on fow e noone no tolnir…óon mo non kulol e teddungal.
\v 16 Mi…óo weltori waawugol hoolorgol on e kala huunde.
\c 8
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Wakkiliniri Mofte …óen fii Okkugol
\p 
\v 1 Men andinay on, yo musi…ì…ìe, fii ndee mo∆¥∆¥ere Alla ye…óaande *mofte makko …óen Masedonii,
\v 2 e maanaa, noone satteendeeji …ói …ìe ndarndaa woo, weltaare ma…ì…ìe heewunde nden e …ìillaare ma…ì…ìe tii…óunde nden no okkude …ìe feere okkirgol no yaajiri.
\v 3 Yeru mbawdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, mi…óo seeditii, …ìe wa…óii hay toonin mbawdi ma…ì…ìe ndin e hoore anniyee mo∆¥∆¥o.
\v 4 ∆Åe landike men, e nder tentingol no tii…óiri, yo …ìe tawde e faabagol yim…ìe Alla …ìen.
\v 5 ∆äun fe∆¥∆¥iti ko men tan∆¥ininoo kon. Kam…ìe tigi …ìe wee…ìitanii Joomi on taho, si …ìe wee…ìitanii men no yaadiri e faale Alla on.
\v 6 Ko …óun wa…ói si men wakkilini Tiituusa yahugol ka mon fii wallugol on laatinde ndee mo∆¥∆¥ere, wano o fu…ó…óornoo non.
\v 7 Wano tawiri non hi…óon mo∆¥∆¥i e …ói fow, ka gom…óinal, ka kongol, ka gandal, ka cataare timmunde, e ka giggol mon e telen-ma amen, mo∆¥∆¥iniree non kadi ndee mo∆¥∆¥ere.
\p 
\v 8 Mi wowliraali …óun fii wa…óugol yamiroore, kono mi wowlan on fii hollugol ba…≤aare …ìeya nden, mi anda si giggol mon ngol ko haqiiqawol.
\v 9 Ko fii hi…óon andi mo∆¥∆¥ere Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, fii kala ko al…óunoo…óo, o wa…óitii baaso fii mon, fii yo baasal makko ngal al…óin on.
\v 10 E hino ko mi miijii no hawrani on kon: ∆Åay ko onon adinoo anniyaade dokkal gila rowani, ko onon adii wa…óugol …óun kadi.
\v 11 Awa jooni, jokkee …óun haa timma, na…ìon haa joofoya, beru wakkilaare mon nden, wondude e anniyee mo aadi…óon on.
\v 12 Si en okkirii anniyee mo∆¥∆¥o, haray …óun ko ko ja…ìetee tippude e ko mar…óen kon, hara hinaa e ko en maraa kon.
\p 
\v 13 Hinaa non fii …ìittingol on, weltina …ìeya, kono ko fii yo fotondiral wa…óu.
\v 14 Fewndo …óoo ko ko …ìurtani on kon won…óon faaborde baasal …ìeya ngal, fii no kam…ìe kadi …ìe faabora baasal mon ngal ko …ìurtani …ìe kon. Si wonirii non, fow fotay,
\v 15 wano windori non:
\q1 ¬´Marnoo…óo buy on wontanii …óun ko hawri,
\q1 on marnoo…óo kadi see…óa, huunde ≈ãakkiraa …óun.¬ª\f g \fr 8:15 \ft 8.15 Egg. 16.18 \f*
\s1 Fii Tiituusa e …ìe o Immindinaa …ìen
\p 
\v 16 Yettoore wonanii Alla fii ko o wa…ói e …ìernde Tiituusa kon sifa cataare nde mi joganii on nden.
\v 17 Fii kala non o ja…ìii e…ì…ìoore an nden fii yo o yahu ka mon, kono hari o aadike, wondude e tinnaare tii…óunde, wonde o yahay kanko tigi ka mon.
\v 18 Men immindinii mo e oo musi…ó…óo mo mofte …óen fow manti fii golle …óe o wa…óani Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o on …óen.
\v 19 E hoore …óun, ko mofte …óen to…ó…óii mo fii ko wona yaadi…ó…óo amen, e nder ndee mo∆¥∆¥ere nde tawata me…óen fawtii fii mangu Joomiraa…óo on tigi, e fii seedintingol anniyeeji amen mo∆¥∆¥i …óin.
\v 20 Me…óen faalaa reenaade fii wota men fele fii ngal dokkal mawngal ngal men halfinaa.
\v 21 Ko fii ko ko mo∆¥∆¥i kon men woni …óa…ì…ìude, hinaa non yeeso Joomiraa…óo on tun, kono kadi e yeeso yim…ìe …ìen.
\p 
\v 22 Men immindinii …ìe e oo musi…ó…óo amen, on mo men ndarndori noone woo cataare makko nden e laabiiji buy, on won…óo …ìanginirde ko tii…ói e ngal …óoo, hoolaare mawnde nde o joganii on nden.
\v 23 Tiituusa non, ko o wondi…ó…óo an e gollidoowo e an fii mon, musi…ì…ìe …ìe o wondi …ìen non, ko …ìe mofte …óen immini, ko …ìe darja *Almasiihu on.\f h \fr 8:23 \ft 8.23 Maa: \it ¬´ko …ìe golloo…ìe fii darja Almasiihu on.¬ª\it*\f*
\v 24 Awa hollee mofte …óen fow dalil giggol mon ngol e ko men woni mantorde fii mon kon yeeso ma…ì…ìe.
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Nafa alaa mi…óo windana on fii ballal fokkintinanaangal yim…ìe Alla …ìen.
\v 2 Awa mi…óo andi anniyee mon mo∆¥∆¥o on fii wallugol, ko fii …óun mi woni mantorde on e yeeso …ìe Masedonii …ìen, mi wi'a wonde, gila rowani …ìee ka diiwal Akaaya no hebulii wallugol. Awa kadi cataare mon nden wakkilinii yim…ìe buy okkugol.
\v 3 Mi imminii …ìee musi…ì…ìe fii wota mantoore nde men mani on nden wonu meere, e yo on wonu hebulii…ìe fii wallugol wano mi wi'iri non.
\v 4 Si tawii men tawoyii on hebulaaki nde min e …ìe Masedonii …ìen men yaadoyi ka mon, haray hoolaare nde men hoolii on nden wontanay men hersa, haray onon hersa mon kan wowlotaako.
\v 5 Awa mi taw no hawri ka mi wakkilina musi…ì…ìe …ìen ka …ìe adoyoo mi ka mon, …ìe wona e fii ballal ngal fodu…óon ngal, fii no ngal hebilora ngal wona okkiraangal anniyee mo∆¥∆¥o, hara hinaa wa si tawii ko kuugal karahaangal.
\s1 Fii Fodaari Wa…óanaandi Aaden Dokko
\p 
\v 6 Andee wonde : mo sankii see…óa ko see…óa o wa'ata, mo sankii buy ko buy o wa'ata.
\v 7 Yo mo kala okkir wano o anniyori non ka …ìernde makko, e …ìaawo ninsugol maa karhegol, ko fii Alla no yi…ói on okkiroowo weltaare.
\v 8 Awa Alla no mari bawgal hebbingol e mon kala noone mo∆¥∆¥ere, fii no he…ìiron saa'i kala ko hatonjin…óon e mun kon fow, e no wa…óiron kadi kala kuugal mo∆¥∆¥al haa fe∆¥∆¥ita,
\v 9 wano windori non wonde:
\q1 ¬´O saakitii dokke,
\q1 o ye…óii miskin…ìe …ìen,
\q1 peewal makko ngal ko luttoowal haa poomaa.¬ª\f i \fr 9:9 \ft 9.9 Zab. 112.9 \f*
\m 
\v 10 On Jonnoowo remoowo on awdi, jonnay mo kadi …≤aametee ko on …≤aama, o ye…óoyay on onon kadi, o sowindirana on awdi ndin, o …ìeyda battane peewal mon ngal.
\v 11 Ko non al…óiniroyte…óon e kala noone fii no waawiron okkirde no yaajiri. Immorde e ngal ballal ngal men hendorta on men hewtina …ìe, …óun adday yettooje Alla.
\v 12 Ko fii ngal ballal ngal wa…óu…óon faaboto yim…ìe Alla …ìen, kono kadi …ìeyday yettooje Alla …óuu…óu…óe.
\v 13 ∆Åay …óee golle mon taskaama, tawaama ko haqiiqaaje, Alla mawninte sabu yankinaare mon nden e telen-ma qirritagol Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o *Almasiihu on, e sabu ballal mon yaajungal ngal wallir…óon …ìe ngal, kam…ìe e yim…ìe …ìen fow.
\v 14 ∆äun, …ìe toranto on wondude e giggol, sabu mo∆¥∆¥ere fe∆¥∆¥itunde nde Alla wa…óani on nden.
\v 15 Yo yettoore wonan Alla fii dokkal makko ngal sifotaako ngal!
\c 10
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Jaabori Aybinoo…ìe Golle makko …óen
\p 
\v 1 Min Puulusa, mi tororii on newaare e mo∆¥∆¥uki *Almasiihu on, min oo newii…óo e yeeso mon, e heewu…óo cuucal fii mon ka wo…ó…óitii on.
\v 2 Awa mi jeejii on, wota on karhan yo mi …ìangin cuucal nde mi hewtoyi ka mon, ko fii mi…óo anniyii seedintinirde hoolaare an nden cuucal e fee …ìen sikku…ìe wonde me…óen wuuriri wa yim…ìe aduna.
\v 3 Hay si tawii wonii ko men yim…ìe aduna, men ha…ìirtaa wano …ìe aduna …ìen gerdata non,
\v 4 ko fii aalaaji …ói men ha…ìirta …óin hinaa …ói oo aduna, kono ko wondu…ói e bawgal iwrungal e Alla fii li…ìugol kala ko dartotoo mo. Men li…ìay miijooji fenaandeeji …óin
\v 5 e kala mawnintinaare hawtotoonde dartoo gandal fii Alla ngal, e men …óahay kala miijo haa ngo …óoftoo Almasiihu on.
\v 6 Si …óoftaare mon nden timmii, me…óen hebulanii kadi donkingol kala ko …óoftaaki.
\p 
\v 7 Awa ndaaree no piiji …óin woniri non. Si go…ó…óo fellitanii hoore mun tigi wonde himo humondiri e Almasiihu on, yo o fellitan hoore makko …óun…óoo: si himo humondiri e Almasiihu on, menen kadi men.
\v 8 E hay si mi mantorii ko …ìurti see…óa mbawdi ndi Joomiraa…óo on ye…ói men ndin fii tabintingol on, hara hinaa fii li…ìugol on, haray mi hersoytaa.
\v 9 Mi faalaaka wa'ude wa hul…ìiniroowo on …ìataake an …óen.
\v 10 Ko fii hi…ìe wi'a: ¬´∆äee …ìataake no tii…ói no …≤aa…ói, kono si tawii kanko himo …óoo, haray himo …óaati, haalaaji makko …óin no mehi…ói.¬ª
\v 11 Kala non jogii…óo ngoo miijo, yo andu fota wonde: kala ko men windani on e …ìaawo mon, ko …óun men wa…óata e tawnde mon.
\p 
\v 12 Men fotondirtaa maa men e…ì…ìindirtaa hoore amen e won…ìe hollitaade …ìen, kono e nder etitagol ma…ì…ìe ngol e e…ì…ìitagol ma…ì…ìe ngol kam…ìe tigi, …óun hollii ko …ìe ≈ãakkiraa…ìe faamu.
\v 13 Menen non, men yi…óaa mawnintinorde ko fe∆¥∆¥iti etirde, kono men fe∆¥∆¥ataa keerol ngol Alla ye…ói men ngol, ko …óun kadi hewtini men haa ka mon.
\v 14 Men fe∆¥∆¥itataa keerol amen ngol, wa si tawii hari men araali haa e mon, ko fii ko goonga, ko haa e mon men ardi e Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o Almasiihu on.
\v 15 Awa men fe∆¥∆¥itirtaa keerol mantorgol golleeji wo…ì…ìe goo, kono me…óen mari tama'u wonde si gom…óinal mon ngal …ìeydike, men waaway kadi laatinde golle …ìur…óe mawnu…óe e hakkunde mon,
\v 16 e nder waajagol e ca'e won…óe toonin mon …óen, …óoo yo men mantor ko wa…óaa kon ka nokkeeli …ìeya.
\v 17 ¬´On mo no mantoo, yo mantor Joomiraa…óo on.¬ª\f j \fr 10:17 \ft 10.17 Yer. 9.23 \f*
\v 18 Ko fii wonaa kulju…óo hoore mun on ja…ìaa, kono ko mo Joomiraa…óo on kulji on.
\c 11
\s1 Fii no Puulusa ∆Åanginiri fii Wa…óitii…ìe Sahaabaa…ìe …ìen
\p 
\v 1 Jooni non, mi…óo tan∆¥inii on waawayno mu…≤…≤anaade lan, mi yewta on haalaaji komoyaagal see…óa. Mi…óo felliti on mu…≤…≤anto lan!
\v 2 Ko fii mi…óo nawlani on nawliigu iwrungu ka Alla, …ìay mi tananike on gorko gooto, fii wee…ìitugol on ka *Almasiihu on, wa jiwo laa…ìu…óo mo andaali gorko.
\v 3 Kono mi…óo huli fota wota on accu miijooji mon …óin selnee e humondiral mon laa…ìungal e haqiiqawal ngal e telen-ma Almasiihu on, wano *Hawaa acciri mboddi ndin …óayniri mo ∆¥oyre mun non.
\v 4 Ko fii si go…ó…óo aru on fe…≤…≤inande fii Iisaajo goo, seedu…óo e mo men fe…≤…≤inani on on, maa si on hendike ruuhu goo seedu…óo e mo hendino…óon on, maa *Linjiila\f k \fr 11:4 \ft 11.4 ∆äun ko Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o on.\f* goo seedu…óo e mo ja…ìuno…óon on, haray on tewtike mo fota.
\v 5 E hin-le mi…óo felliti, …ìen ¬´sahaabaa…ìe townitii…ìe¬ª …ìuraa lan hay huunde.
\v 6 Fii kala mi…óo hesi…óani waajagol, kono mi hesi…óanaa gandal ngal, men hollirii on …óun noone fow e …ói fow.
\p 
\v 7 Kaa hara mi wa…óii junuubu fewndo mi …óuytitii fii …ìantugol on, wa fewndo ko mi fe…≤…≤inani on Kibaaru Mo∆¥∆¥o on e …ìaawo ∆¥antugol on hay huunde?
\v 8 Mi ittinii *mofte goo fii he…ìirgol …ìe njoddi fii wallitagol on.
\v 9 E hin-le fewndo mi ≈ãakkiraa ka mon, mi wonaano dongal hay gooto, ko fii musi…ì…ìe iwru…ìe Masedonii …ìen faaboranno ko mi ≈ãakkiraa kon fow. Mi reenino wonugol dongal mon, e mi …ìurtay-le reenaade e …óun.
\v 10 Fodde goonga Almasiihu on no e an, mi…óo wi'i: hay gooto fannataa lan mantorgol …óun e nder diiwal Akaaya ngal fow.
\v 11 Fii hon…óun non? Hara ko fii mi yi…óaa on? Alla no andi mi…óo yi…ói on.
\p 
\v 12 Ko mi woni wa…óude kon, mi jokkay wa…óugol …óun kadi, fii ha…óugol …ìen faalaa…ìe mantorde fotugol e amen.
\v 13 ∆Åen ko wa…óitii…ìe sahaabaa…ìe, golloo…ìe …óaynoo…ìe, wa…óinkinii…ìe sahaabaa…ìe Almasiihu on.
\v 14 Kono …óun ≈ãal…óinaa, ko fii Ibuliisa tigi ko wa…óinkinotoo…óo malaa'ikaajo ndaygu.
\v 15 Haray juhaa kadi ka golloo…ìe makko …ìen wa…óinkinoo golloo…ìe peewal. Kono rawnoode ma…ì…ìe nden wa'ay wa kuu…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen.
\s1 Fii Golleeji e Tampereeji Puulusa …óin
\p 
\v 16 Awa mi…óo fillitaade kadi: wota gooto ndaariran wa komoojo. Si hinaa …óun, jogoree lan wa komoojo, fii min kadi no mi mantora see…óa.
\v 17 Ko mi woni wowlude koo e nder hoolaare he…ìugol ko mi mantora, hinaa ko iwri e Joomiraa…óo on, kono ko wa komoojo.
\v 18 ∆Åay …óuu…óu…ìe no mantorde piiji aduna, min kadi mi mantoray …óun.
\v 19 Awa, onon mar…ìe faamu …ìen, on mu…≤…≤anto no newori komoo…ìe …ìen!
\v 20 Hi…óon mu…≤…≤aade kadi ko kurkete…óon kon e ko huutorte…óon kon e ko jattete…óon kon e ko jogorte…óon mawnintinaare kon e hay banteede.
\v 21 Me…óen hersi wi'ugol wonde me…óen lo'i e telen-ma …óii piiji!
\p Kala ko go…ó…óo suusi mantorde, haray min kadi mi…óo suusi, (ko wa komoojo mi woni wowlirde).
\v 22 Si ko …ìe *Aabirayankee…ìe? Awa min kadi men. Si ko …ìe *Isra'iilayankee…ìe? Awa min kadi men. Si ko …ìe jurriya Ibraahiima? Awa min kadi men.
\v 23 Kaa ko …ìe kurkaa…ói Almasiihu on? Awa mi…óo yewtirde komoyaagal, min kadi ko mi …ìuri …óun! Telen-ma ka golleeji mi…óo …ìuri …ìe, ka kaseede mi…óo …ìuri …ìe, ka piyeede, …óon kadi mi…óo …ìuri …ìe, soono woo mi…óo wee…ìitanii mayde.
\v 24 Laabi jowi mi…óo he…ìirde Yahuudiyankee…ìe …ìen paatawol cappan…óe nay ≈ãakku…óun ngol gooto!
\v 25 Laabi tati mi…óo luuboreede bedi, mi fi…óaa kaa∆¥e nde wootere, laabi tati mi tawaa e nder laa…óe won…óe lancaade, mi wonii kadi ka ndiyan …≤allal gootal e jemma gooto, mi…óo aw∆¥a.
\v 26 Soono woo e nder jinduruuji an …óin haray mi…óo wee…ìitanii masiibooji …óin ka maaje, e masiibooji hippotoo…ìe …ìen, e masiibooji yim…ìe le…≤ol an ngol, e masiibooji …ìe wonaa Yahuudiyanke …ìen, e masiibooji …óin ka ca'e, e masiibooji …óin ka wulaaji, e masiibooji …óin ka baharu, e masiibooji wi'itii…ìe …ìen ko men musi…ì…ìe,
\v 27 e ka golle e ka satteende, e jemmaaji …ói …óaanaaka, e heege e …óonka e ≈ãakkireede …≤aametee, e jaangol e kolngal!\f m \fr 11:27 \ft 11.27 Maa: \it ¬´kolndan.¬ª\it*\f*
\v 28 E hoore mi wowlaali fii ko heddii e dongal ngal mi rondii …≤ande woo fii aanangol mofte …óen fow.
\v 29 Si go…ó…óo lo'ii, hewtay lan. Si go…ó…óo yanii e junuubu, ko min muusata.
\p 
\v 30 Si tawii bee mi mantoo, haray ko fii lo'ere an nden mi mantotoo.
\v 31 Alla, on won…óo Ben Iisaa Joomi on, on mo mantoore wonani haa poomaa, no andi wonde mi fenataa.
\v 32 Oo lan…óo Damaasi wi'etee…óo Aretaasa ittayno ko ayna saare Damaasiyankoo…ìe …ìen fii nangugol lan.
\v 33 Kono mi tumbaa e debeere, mi tippiniraa e yolnde, jokkinaa maadi ndin, ko nii mi fuutori …ìe.
\c 12
\s1 Fii Fe…≤…≤inaneede Puulusa
\p 
\v 1 Bee mi mantoo, fii kala …óun nafataa. Kono fow e mun yo mi yewtu fii wirnitan…óe e fe…≤…≤inan…óe iwru…óe ka Joomiraa…óo on.
\v 2 Wonii nii duu…ìi sappoo e nay mi…óo andi go…ó…óo gom…óin…óo *Almasiihu on, na…ìanoo…óo ka kammu tata…ìu,\f n \fr 12:2 \ft 12.2 Ko Puulusa tigi woni on go…ó…óo mo o woni wowlude fii mun.\f* (mi andaa non si ko kanko tigi maa si ko ruuhu makko on, kono Alla ka…≤un no andi).
\v 3-4 Ko mi andi tun, on na…ìaama ka aljanna, o nanii kongu…ói …ói sifotaako, …ói newnanaaka ne…ó…óo fillagol, (mi andaa non si tawii ko kanko tigi maa si tawii ko ruuhu makko on, kono Alla ka…≤un no andi).
\v 5 Ko sifa on ne…ó…óo mi mantorta, kono mi mantortaa hoore an tigi, si hinaa fii lo'ereeji an …óin.
\v 6 Si tawii mi…óo faalaa mantaade, mi wonataa komoojo, ko fii mi wowloyay goonga, kono mi mantotaako, fii wota go…ó…óo tuuman toonin ko o woni yi'irde lan kon, maa ko o woni lan nanirde kon.
\v 7 Sabu …óee fe…≤…≤inan…óe maw…óe …óe mi fe…≤…≤inanaa, mi he…ìuno ko tampinirimmi wa bullal ka …ìandu an fii wota mi manto, …óun ko mo Ibuliisa imminnoo fii tampingol lan.
\v 8 Laabiiji tati mi…óo jeejude Joomiraa…óo on yo o wo…ó…óintinan …óun,
\v 9 o jaabii lan: ¬´Mo∆¥∆¥ere an nden yonii ma, ko fii bawgal an ngal ko e nder lo'ere nden …ìangata.¬ª Awa mi …ìeyday mantaade fii lo'ereeji an …óin, fii no bawgal Almasiihu on wonira e hoore an.
\v 10 Ko …óun wa…ói si mi…óo weltii fii lo'ereeji …óin e hoyreeji …óin e sattendeeji …óin e cukkan…óe …óen e anndeeji …óin fii Almasiihu on. Ko fii, nde mi laatii lo'u…óo, ko onsay mi woni dolnu…óo.
\s1 Fii Annde nde Puulusa Joganii …ìe Korenti …ìen nden
\p 
\v 11 Mi wa'uno wa komoojo, kono ko onon karhunoo mi, …ìay ko onon haanuno kuljude lan! Ko fii hay huunde mi seedaa e …ìen ¬´sahaabaa…ìe townitii…ìe¬ª, fii kala hinaa mi huunde.
\v 12 Maandeeji hollu…ói fii sahaabaa…ìe …ìen wa…óiraama yeeso mon ≈ãa…≤…≤annde tii…óunde, …óun ko maandeeji e kuu…óe e kaawakeeji mo∆¥∆¥i.
\v 13 Ko hon…óun …óeya *mofte he…ìi ko on he…ìaali, si wonaa mi wonanaali on dongal? Awa yaafanee lan on ella …óon!
\p 
\v 14 Awa e hino, mi…óo faalaa yahude ka mon tammun, e hoore mi wonoytaa dongal mon, ko fii mi alaa …óa…ì…ìude ko mon kon, kono ko onon tigi, …ìay hinaa paykoy koy haani marande maw…ìe mun …ìen, kono ko maw…ìe …ìen haani marande fay…ìe mun …ìen.
\v 15 Min mi wonay anniyii…óo fii fawtagol, e mi fawtoto hoore an fii wonkiiji mon …óin. Si mi …ìurtii on yi…óude, e hara giggol mon ngol e telen-ma an …óuytoto?
\v 16 Awa, mi wonanaali on dongal. E hara mi laatike ne…ó…óo ∆¥oy…óo? Kaa mi hendorii on janfa?
\v 17 Kaa mi rewii e go…ó…óo e …ìe mi imminani on …ìen fii huutorgol on?
\v 18 Awa, mi wakkilinii Tiituusa fii yahugol ka mon, mi immindinii mo e musi…ó…óo goo. Enee, taw si hara Tiituusa huutorii on onon fii he…ìugol go…ó…óun? E taw si hara kadi men jokkaali anniyee gooto e e…ì…ìooje goote?
\p 
\v 19 No gasa hi…óon sikka gila nee…ìii wonde men danditoto woni e telen-ma mon. Awa, ko yeeso Alla e innde Almasiihu on men woni yewtirde. ∆äun fow non, yo yi…ì…ìe, ko fii tii…óingol on.
\v 20 Ko fii mi…óo huli, nde mi hewtoyi, no gasa mi tawroya on hara hinaa no mi faaliraa non, e min kadi no gasa hara hinaa no faalira…óon non. Mi…óo huli wota taw no gasa hara ko yeddondiral e nawliigu e monee e haasidi e …≤oore e baddi e mawnintinaare e jii…ìoldu woni hakkunde mon.
\v 21 Mi…óo huli, nde mi hewtoyi ka mon, wota Alla an on hersinoyan kadi e yeeso mon, mi wona e yoomugol fii wa…óunoo…ìe junuubu …óuu…óu…ìe, …ìe ronki tuubude ngal angal laa…ìal e jinaa e jii…ìaare nde …ìe wa…ói nden.
\c 13
\s1 Fii Hajan…óe Puulusa Sakkitore …óen
\p 
\v 1 Mi…óo yahude ka mon tammun. Kala kongol …≤aawiroyte kongu…ói seedee…ìe …ói…óo maa tato.
\v 2 Wa fewndo ko mi wonnoo ka mon …óimmun, hari mi wowliino …óun. Awa hande kadi, ka tawata mi alaa ton, mi wowlanii …óun kadi wa…óunoo…ìe junuubu …ìen ado mi yahude: si mi yiltoyike ka mon mi woopoytaa hay gooto,
\v 3 ko fii hi…óon …óa…ì…ìude seedee wonde ko *Almasiihu on woni longinde lan ko mi woni wowlude kon, on mo lo'aa e telen-ma mon, kono mar…óo bawgal e hakkunde mon.
\v 4 Ko fii fewndo Almasiihu on fempanoo, hari ko o lo'u…óo, kono jooni himo wuuriri bawgal Alla ngal. Menen kadi e nder humondiral amen e makko, ko men lo'u…ìe, kono menen e makko men wuuriray bawgal Alla ngal fii mon.
\v 5 Awa taskee hoore mon onon tigi fii andugol si hi…óon wuuriri gom…óinal, ndarndito…óon onon tigi. E on andaa Iisaa Almasiihu on no e mon? Si hinaa taw on woopu ndarnditagol mon ngol.
\v 6 Kono mi…óo tan∆¥inii on taway wonde en woopaali ndarnditagol men ngol.
\v 7 Ko e nder …óun men torotoo Alla fii wota on wa…óu huunde ko boni. Hinaa non fii hollugol wonde men felnaaki, kono ko fii yo on wa…óu ko mo∆¥∆¥i, hay si tawii menen me…óen wa'i wa woopu…ìe.
\v 8 Ko fii men waawanaa goonga on hay huunde. Kono ko wonangol goonga on men waawi.
\v 9 Menen men weltoto nde men lo'i, e hin-le onon hi…óon dolni, e ko men yelotoo e nder torndeeji amen …óin, ko fii no laatoron timmu…ìe.
\v 10 Ko …óun wa…ói si mi…óo windande on …óun si mi alaa ton, fii nde mi aroyi, wota mi sattiniran on huutorgol mbawdi fii laamagol on ndi Joomiraa…óo on ye…óimmi ndin fii tii…óingol on, hara hinaa fii li…ìugol on.
\s1 Fii Rawnoode ∆Åatakuru ndun e Salminaango mun
\p 
\v 11 Fii rawnagol, yo musi…ì…ìe, wonee e nder weltaare, e…ì…ìanee wonugol timmu…ìe, wakkilindiron, he…ìon miijo wooto, wondiron …ìuttu. ∆äun, Alla Jom giggol e …ìuttu on wonday e mon.
\p 
\v 12 Salmondiree, hirbondiron hirbondiral laa…ìungal. Awa kadi gom…óin…ìe …ìen fow salminii on.
\v 13 Yo mo∆¥∆¥ere Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi on, e giggol Alla, wonu e mon on fow, wondude e humondiral e *Ruuhu Senii…óo on.
